title: My boards level mix up
body: I am level 23, I am currently level 6 in the boards.

replies.body: Looks like your post here sync'd up your profile!  Our [syncing tool ](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/fos1aFEB-boards-profile-syncing-tool) is available as well, but everything looks okay now!
